                <p>Sit with Family or Friends – Higher boarding priority increases the chances of sitting together.</p>
                <p>More Overhead Bin Space – Board earlier and secure space for your carry-on luggage.</p>
                <h2>How Much Does Early Bird Check-In Cost?</h2>
                <p>This is only $15 – $25 per person per flight segment (Price varies based on demand and route).</p>
                <h3>How to Purchase Early Bird Check-In?</h3>
                <p>You can buy Early Bird Check-In:</p>
                <p>During flight booking on Southwest’s website or app.</p>
                <p>After booking (up to 36 hours before departure).</p>
