                <p>Families and groups who want to sit together can become part of Southwest Airlines' early bird check-in program.</p>
                <p>Passengers who have large luggage with them and want to avoid the last-minute hassles.</p>
                <p>You can avail the stress-free check-in experience while using this service by the airline.</p>
